Hi Matt,

I just wanted to let you know I was contacted by a blood relative of Dawnde=
e's, a great aunt. The team has agreed to let her and her husband be placem=
ent for the children so they went over the weekend. I went to see them yest=
erday and they are doing great and seem to be very happy there. I never did=
 hear from your brother.

Also, I am wondering if you have heard anything from your attorney? I still=
 have not heard anything from her. With court next week, I was hoping that =
maybe you had been able to make contact with her. I did copy her on the e-m=
ail I sent to you with the new date and time for court.

Thank You,

Jennifer Emmons
Social Services Unit Supervisor
(417)629-3896


